title: 'Daily Show' contributor tells CNN about experience at MAGA rally
description: CNN's Jim Acosta talks to "The Daily Show with Trevor Noah" contributor Jordan Klepper about the MAGA rally he attended in Mississippi where Klepper talked to Trump supporters about Jan. 6 and the Congressional hearing.

title: 245 years later, has the 'American experiment' begun to fail?
description: As the January 6 hearing continues, CNN's Jake Tapper examines whether the "American experiment," a phrase coined in the New-York Daily Tribune in 1860, can withstand the current political atmosphere.

title: Is Russia winning? Hear US Secretary of State's response
description: CNN's Jake Tapper interviews US Secretary of State Antony Blinken at the G7 summit in Germany to discuss Russian President Vladimir Putin and Russia's war in Ukraine.

title: World leaders caught on camera mocking Putin at meeting
description: UK Prime Minister Boris Johnson and Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau poked fun at Russian President Vladimir Putin's infamous bare-chested  photos at a G7 meeting in Krün, Germany.

title: Never mind China's new aircraft carrier, these are the ships the US should worry about
description: China made a big statement about its naval ambitions with the recent launch of its third and most advanced aircraft carrier.
